        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You gain the unarmed attack listed for your ancestry. At your GM's discretion, you can select one of the alternate unarmed attack options listed in the Less Standard Unarmed Attacks sidebar.</p>\n<p>At 5th level, whenever you land a critical hit with one of these attacks, you can add its critical specialization effect.</p><hr /><p><strong>Special</strong> If you have multiple attacks listed for your ancestry, you can take this feat up to the number of attacks listed for your ancestry. Each time you do, select a different attack.</p>"
